```
Next, create a controller named `ResetPasswordController` in `app/Http/Controllers` folder. Inside this controller, create a `reset` method as shown below:
```php
<?php

namespace App\Http\Controllers;

use Illuminate\Foundation\Auth\ResetsPasswords;

class ResetPasswordController extends Controller
{
    /*
    |--------------------------------------------------------------------------
    | Password Reset Controller
